---
title: Loaded Chicken Green Veggie Soup & Herby Panini with Basil Pesto & Parmesan Cheese
description: A steaming bowl of green soup is the perfect cure for whatever ails you! Packed with green veggies and punchy flavours, this
meal provides the key to a cosy night in. Tear into a toasty, garlicky panini and dunk it in for even more flavour and crunch!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
